In Spanish ]

652
00:48:11,188 --> 00:48:16,057
He's says he wants to eat.
He's much hungry
from so much of the talk.

653
00:48:19,864 --> 00:48:21,798
Thank you.

654
00:48:21,866 --> 00:48:24,596
Why, look!
Fresh beef.

655
00:48:24,668 --> 00:48:27,694
Oh, Ma.
Fix up a spread for everybody.

656
00:48:27,771 --> 00:48:31,070
Can't call it stealin',
because at the time of death
there won't be any owners.

657
