We got 'em, Sheriff.

845
01:06:40,040 --> 01:06:42,600
- It's all right.
Everything's been attended to.
- What are you talking about?

846
01:06:42,676 --> 01:06:44,735
Kinkaid's murderers,
we got all three of'em.

847
01:06:44,811 --> 01:06:47,405
Yeah,
and we hung 'em too, Sheriff.

848
01:06:47,481 --> 01:06:50,382
- Aaah!
- Larry Kinkaid's not dead!

849
01:06:53,453 --> 01:06:56,752
- Not dead?
- But we just--

850
01:06:56,823 --> 01:06:59,451
I just left Larry Kinkaid
with the doctor at Pike's Hole.

851
01:06:59,526 --> 01:07:02,324
- Caught the fellas
who shot him too.
- But, Sheriff.

852
01:07:02,395 --> 01:07:05,296
They had Larry's
cattle down there.
They even had his gun.

853
01:07:05,365 --> 01:07:08,266
Give me that badge.

854
01:07:08,335 --> 01:07:10,701
Mr. Davies, I know you
well enough to know...

855
01:07:10,770 --> 01:07:12,931
that you didn't have
anything to do with this.

856
01:07:13,006 --> 01:07:16,032
I'm depending on you
to tell me who did.

857
01:07:29,202 --> 01:07:31,534
All but seven.

858
01:07:34,007 --> 01:07:37,773
God better have mercy on ya.
You won't get any from me.

859
01:07:37,844 --> 01:07:39,778
All right. Let's go.

860
01:07:52,459 --> 01:07:54,450
If you've got
no objections, Mr. Davies...

861
01:07:54,528 --> 01:07:56,519
I'd like to read
Martin's letter now.

862
01:07:56,596 --> 01:07:59,793
It would be a good idea
if a lot of people read it.

863
01:08:47,347 --> 01:08:51,044
If you ask me, that Tetley's
the one we ought to lynch.

864
01:08:52,852 --> 01:08:55,912
You're a great one for hangin',
ain't ya, Smith?

