866
01:09:20,213 --> 01:09:22,147
[ Rattling Continues ]

867
01:09:25,118 --> 01:09:28,645
You loved it.
That's why you kept them
waiting so long.

868
01:09:28,722 --> 01:09:31,987
I saw your face.
It was the face of a depraved,
murderous beast.

869
01:09:32,058 --> 01:09:34,959
<i>There are only two things</i>
<i>that have ever meant</i>
<i>anything to you</i>--

870
01:09:35,028 --> 01:09:37,087
<i>power and cruelty.</i>

871
01:09:37,163 --> 01:09:39,825
<i>You can't feel pity.</i>
<i>You can't even feel guilt.</i>

872
01:09:39,899 --> 01:09:43,494
<i>You knew those men</i>
<i>were innocent,yet you were</i>
<i>crazy to see them hanged...</i>

873
01:09:43,570 --> 01:09:46,471
to make me watch it.

874
01:09:46,539 --> 01:09:50,305
I could've stopped you
with a gun,just as any animal
could be stopped from killing...

875
01:09:50,377 --> 01:09:52,777
but I couldn't do it
because I'm a coward.

876
01:09:52,846 --> 01:09:55,178
[ Laughs ]

877
01:09:55,248 --> 01:09:58,046
Aren't you glad
you made me go, Father?

878
01:09:58,118 --> 01:10:00,450
Weren't you proud of me?

879
01:10:00,520 --> 01:10:02,852
How does it feel to have begot
a weakling, Major Tetley?

880
01:10:02,922 --> 01:10:06,221
<i>Does it make you afraid</i>
<i>that there may be</i>
<i>some weakness in you too...</i>

881
01:10:06,292 --> 01:10:09,125
<i>that other men might discover</i>
<i>and whisper about?</i>

882
01:10:09,195 --> 01:10:11,925
<i>Open the door, Major.</i>
<i>I want to see your face!.</i>

883
01:10:11,998 --> 01:10:14,228
<i>I want to know</i>
<i>how you feel now!.</i>

884
01:10:18,038 --> 01:10:20,006
<i>[ Gunshot ]</i>

885
01:11:16,396 --> 01:11:20,127
They're getting up a pot
for Martin's wife.

886
01:11:20,200 --> 01:11:23,192
Even Mapes chipped in.

887
01:11:23,269 --> 01:11:25,863
I didn't know
he was showin' his face.

888
01:11:25,939 --> 01:11:28,499
He ain't.
He sent it by Sparks.

889
01:11:31,010 --> 01:11:34,969
That reminds me,
I put in $25 bucks apiece for us.

890
01:11:35,048 --> 01:11:39,075
- How much they got?
- About five hundred.

891
01:11:39,152 --> 01:11:42,713
Hmph. Not bad for a husband
who don't know any better...

892
01:11:42,789 --> 01:11:47,123
than to buy cattle in the spring
without a bill of sale.

893
01:11:53,399 --> 01:11:56,732
Maybe you ought to read
this letter too.

894
01:11:56,803 --> 01:11:59,067
You know I can't read.

895
01:12:12,919 --> 01:12:15,547
I'll read it to ya.

896
01:12:17,423 --> 01:12:22,554
""My Dear Wife, Mr. Davies will tell you
what's happening here tonight.

897
01:12:22,629 --> 01:12:25,655
""He's a good man and has done
everything he can for me.

898
01:12:25,732 --> 01:12:28,633
""I suppose there are
some other good men here too...

899
01:12:28,701 --> 01:12:31,534
""only they don't seem
to realize what they're doing.

900
01:12:31,604 --> 01:12:34,300
""They're the ones
I feel sorry for...

901
01:12:34,374 --> 01:12:36,706
<i>""'cause it'll be over</i>
<i>for me in a little while...</i>

902
01:12:36,776 --> 01:12:40,177
<i>""but they'll have to go on rememberin'</i>
<i>for the rest of their lives.</i>

903
01:12:40,246 --> 01:12:44,080
<i>""Man just naturally can't take</i>
<i>the law into his own hands...</i>

904
01:12:44,150 --> 01:12:47,449
<i>""and hang people</i>
<i>without hurting everybody</i>
<i>in the world...</i>

905
01:12:47,520 --> 01:12:52,423
<i>""'cause then he's notjust</i>
<i>breaking one law but all laws.</i>

906
01:12:52,492 --> 01:12:56,451
""Law's a lot more than
words you put in a book...

907
01:12:56,529 --> 01:13:00,431
""or judges or lawyers or sheriffs
you hire to carry it out.

908
01:13:00,500 --> 01:13:04,960
""It's everything people
ever have found out
about justice...

909
01:13:05,038 --> 01:13:07,268
""and what's right and wrong.

910
01:13:07,340 --> 01:13:11,106
""It's the very conscience
of humanity.

911
01:13:11,177 --> 01:13:16,308
""There can't be such a thing
as civilization unless people
have a conscience...

912
01:13:16,382 --> 01:13:19,840
""because if people
touch God anywhere...

913
01:13:19,919 --> 01:13:22,888
""where is it except
through their conscience?

914
01:13:22,956 --> 01:13:26,323
""And what is
anybody's conscience
except a little piece...

915
01:13:26,392 --> 01:13:29,020
""of the conscience
of all men that ever lived?

916
01:13:32,065 --> 01:13:35,091
""I guess that's all
I've got to say except...

917
01:13:35,168 --> 01:13:37,966
""kiss the babies for me
and God bless you.

918
01:13:38,037 --> 01:13:40,028
Your husband, Donald.''

919
01:13:45,044 --> 01:13:48,536
olol<i>[ Organ:: ""Red River Valley'"]</i>

920
01:14:16,609 --> 01:14:19,442
Where are we goin'?

921
01:14:19,512 --> 01:14:22,640
He said he wanted his wife
to get this letter, didn't he?

922
01:14:22,715 --> 01:14:27,084
Said there was nobody
to look after the kids, didn't he?

923
01:14:30,823 --> 01:14:32,848
